name: Spiraltz
description:
Spiraltz is unique for each user, as Spiraltz uses your wallet address as the seed for generation. Even though you can make modifications with the sliders, your Spiraltz will always remain unique. If you aren't synced, you will see a random sample Spiraltz.

Left click to show/hide your address.
Right click to save a seamless 4s gif of your Spiraltz.
